 "body": "<p>S681A-S681AN Income Tax Act 2007 (ITA 2007), S834-S848 Corporation Tax Act 2010 (CTA 2010)</p>\n\n<p>This section is about legislation which counters certain avoidance devices based on arrangements for the sale and leaseback of land or any interest in land. There are two anti-avoidance rules which:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>limit the deduction for payments under the lease to a commercial rent, and</li>\n  <li>deal with the situation where a lessee incurs additional rental liability for a comparatively short period in return for the payment of a lump sum.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>This chapter contains the following:</p>\n",
